@startuml
actor Actor
participant "UI: React" as UI
participant "AuthMiddleware" as Auth
participant "MemberController" as Ctrl
participant "MemberService" as Svc
participant "UserRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

Actor -> UI: Clic en "Desactivar" miembro
UI -> UI: Mostrar diálogo de confirmación (BR-MEM-03)
Actor -> UI: Confirmar
UI -> Auth: DELETE /api/members/{userId}
Auth -> Auth: Validar jerarquía (BR-MEM-02)
Auth -> Ctrl: deactivateMember(userId)
Ctrl -> Svc: deactivateMember(userId)
Svc -> Repo: findById(userId)
Repo --> Svc: User Entity
Svc -> Svc: user.status = INACTIVE
Svc -> Repo: save(user)
Repo -> DB: UPDATE users SET status = 'inactive' ...
DB --> Repo: OK
Svc --> Ctrl: Success
Ctrl --> Auth: 200 OK
Auth --> UI: Success Message
UI --> Actor: Actualiza lista de miembros
@enduml
